<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q19_v13" title="Q19_v13" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceA</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>Selecciona la opción que muestra una expresión equivalente a 
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>9</m:mn>
            <m:mo>·</m:mo>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:mfrac>
                <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn>
              </m:mfrac>
            </m:mrow>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>7</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>.
      </qti-prompt>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>7</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, esta expresión es equivalente.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:msqrt>
            <m:mfrac>
              <m:mn>7</m:mn>
              <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            </m:mfrac>
          </m:msqrt>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La expresión original vale <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>, mientras que esta opción es <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mfrac><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:msqrt></m:math>. Además, <m:math><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>63</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y <m:math><m:mrow><m:msup><m:msqrt><m:mfrac><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>63</m:mn></m:math> y <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> no son iguales, las expresiones no son equivalentes.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mfrac>
              <m:mn>1</m:mn>
              <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            </m:mfrac>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>63</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esta opción vale <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:msqrt><m:mn>63</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. En cambio, la expresión original vale <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math> y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math> no son iguales, no es equivalente.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>9</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mfrac>
                <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn>
              </m:mfrac>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esta opción es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mfrac><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. Si se eleva al cuadrado, se obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mfrac><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:msqrt></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>81</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>189</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. En cambio, la expresión original vale <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math> y su cuadrado es <m:math><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>63</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>189</m:mn></m:math> y <m:math><m:mn>63</m:mn></m:math> no son iguales, no es una expresión equivalente.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Simplificación de la expresión</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar la expresión original</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión dada es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Multiplicar los factores numéricos</strong></p>
            <p>Primero se calcula:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Escribir la expresión simplificada</strong></p>
            <p>Reemplazando ese resultado en la expresión:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Esto también se puede escribir como:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Comparar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p>La alternativa A muestra exactamente <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>La alternativa C no es igual, porque <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:msqrt><m:mn>63</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Las alternativas B y D tampoco coinciden con <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión equivalente es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, por lo tanto la respuesta correcta es la alternativa A.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>